DOC.brief_summary: The study aims to investigate the effect of Acu-TENS on post-exercise blood lactate level and EPOC
DOC.brief_title: Effects of Acu-Transcutaneous Electrical Nerve Stimulation (Acu-TENS) on Post-exercise Blood Lactate and Excessive Post-exercise Oxygen Consumption (EPOC)
DOC.criteria: with normal health (no known history of cardiovascular, pulmonary, metabolic or musculoskeletal diseases) unable to communicate and follow the exercise procedures
